CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, March 7, 1959, pg. 13 reads: "Young Models - Rosenbaum's teen-age models last Saturday included these lovely young girls. Rosenbaum's Department Store features various young models from different clubs in various fashion shows.  Last week, two of the members of Centre Avenue YMCA's Les Voguettes Charm Club of which Mrs. Bernice Burrell is supervisor, were included.  Seated, left to right, are Barbara Drugmand, Patricia Wray, Easter Buun [sic] JoAnne Richards; Mary Trimble, Sandy Baylor and Maie Dempsey.  Standing: Mary Ellen Nardosi, Mary Ellen Blaine, Rena Rice, Jo Ann Stamicar, Nancy Gillett, Gwen Williams, Barbara Lee Humbic and Barbara Toney. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of models for Rosenbaum's Department Store, seated, left to right: Barbara Drugmand, Patricia Wray, Easter Bunny JoAnne Richards, Mary Trimble, Sandy Baylor, and Maie Dempsey; standing: Mary Ellen Nardosi, Mary Ellen Blaine, Rena Rice, Jo Ann Stamicar, Nancy Gillett, Gwen Williams, Barbara Lee Humbic, and Barbara Toney, gathered on stage
